      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy. The exterior shows substantial wear, including advanced rust on the wheel wells, several large dents, and widespread paint oxidation. Inside, the cabin has seen better days; the upholstery is heavily stained and torn, and several interior trim pieces are missing or broken. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and there are multiple fluid leaks that need immediate attention. The transmission shifts harshly, and the suspension requires a complete overhaul. This car is ideal as a donor vehicle for parts or a dedicated project for an experienced mechanic prepared for a full restoration.",
