      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original factory depth and gloss without a single scratch, dent, or swirl mark. Every panel gap is perfect, and all trim pieces are in pristine condition. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the upholstery shows no signs of wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and all electronic features function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously serviced on a strict schedule with full documentation. It drives perfectly, with a smooth engine and tight suspension. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade example that has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather.",
